        <title>Memorandum</title>
        <para id="id25319222">Vertebrates and invertebrates</para>
        <para id="id25383792">Fish, amphibians, reptiles, birds, mammals</para>
        <para id="id25383796">Common chacteristic (p. 10): invertebrate</para>
        <para id="id25383801">Table:</para>
        <para id="id25281051">1. Starfish, sea anemone</para>
        <para id="id25281057">2. Mussel, snail, octopus</para>
        <para id="id25387870">3. Earthworm</para>
        <para id="id25387876">4. Locust, cricket, cicada</para>
        <para id="id21225688">5. Tick, spider, scorpion</para>
