        <para id="id25280425"><emphasis effect="bold">Reason:</emphasis> presence or absence of exoskeleton (external skeleton) or articulated legs</para>
        <para id="id24810612">Assignment 2:</para>
        <para id="id25396758"><emphasis effect="bold">Key:</emphasis> There are always two options, selection of an option must lead to insects. The following features must be included: invertebrate, arthropod, exoskeleton, six legs.</para>
